    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. This driver-focused example has been meticulously maintained, with documented rod bearing replacement and a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural integrity under load. The dual-VANOS system has been overhauled for precise variable valve timing, and the factory limited-slip differential provides exceptional traction out of apexes. Upgraded with Bilstein B16 dampers and fresh bushings, the chassis offers sharp turn-in and communicative feedback. A well-sorted machine that prioritizes performance and mechanical longevity.",
